Update Your Analytics App

You can update the Engagement Analytics App to the latest version if it becomes out of date.

Workforce Engagement is available in Lightning Experience and requires Enterprise, Performance, or Unlimited Editions.

When enabled, Workforce Engagement Management installs the Analytics App automatically. If the app is outdated, an alert appears on the Analytics Dashboard page with a message to update the template version.

To reinstall the Analytics App:

From Setup, enter "Workforce Engagement Management" in the Quick Find box and select Getting Started.
If the installed version of the Analytics app isn't the latest, click Reinstall or Update.
Click Refresh.
title: Updating Workforce Engagement Analytics App
